Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both dense in the head, \Nand fragile in a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bungler, plus terribly short-tempered! {flying into a rage; losing one's cool​}
