Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Perspective-Changing Spectacles Good-Bad-kun. {見方変換めがみ善悪ん}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When wearing them this way, you can only see \Neveryone's bad sides, and can't stop badmouthing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you turn them around, you start seeing \Neveryone's good sides and become all-loving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a dangerous tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really how Taru looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's somehow repulsing this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Do you find joy in constantly harassing me with your weird magic gizmos that get me in all sorts of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't, Honmaru! \NI only ever use magic for your good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! For my good? I ain't buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! You use magic to mess with me \Nto make me into a bad guy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Always pulling that cute and innocent act. {woman or girl who acts cute by playing innocent and helpless​}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with those fat puffy cheeks, huh? {not really sure how puffy cheeks can be an insult; assumed なんだそのぱんぱんにはったほっぺ たよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep and keep slandering him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the most disgusting type of guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep crying, you wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru came to hate me... Hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Taru! \NI don't know what's gotten into me just now! {unsure, maybe "what was I saying just now" or anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I say. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Using these spectacles involves a bit of danger, \Nbut it's just what I need against Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the look of a demon in your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And where did this come from? {/what are you saying so suddenly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't even realize that ribbon \Nis not one bit becoming to your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny how you're usually the one so igno... {短足 but I don't see what it may have to do with "short-leggedness"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you sure have one twisted friggin' personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're actually a "faint of heart" kinda girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So to keep it a secret, \Nyou turn to hurting others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Pardon my frankness, but you're a mess, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Honmaru? \NTelling me things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the kinda fella you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me the black magician of words now! {/thaumaturge }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Jabao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I praised you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you! How can you be so gutless, Korekiyo? {weak; feeble; weak-willed; cowardly; gutless}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna play with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eck! And you have a face like a worn-out boot! \NYour hair's growing like an eggplant! {/Your head has a hair-growing ability of an eggplant!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In class, you're the only one \Nuniversally hated by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Some just hang out with you reluctantly, \Nknowing you'll beat 'em up otherwise{/if you get mad}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have absolutely zero merit to you, \Nand you're stupid to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Also with 30 kilograms of fat in that belly. {tlc, no clue what's グラム30** here, was "shibou ha guramu sanjuu da" in manga; assumed it's just a weird contraction of "kilograms"} {9:21: I'm hearing その腹の脂肪はグラム三十いん\NI can't make out the word at the end but I think what you have now is fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, just as I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Brandishing your strength as soon as you have a chance! \NThat's exactly what everyone hates you for! {/resorting to violence} {unsure what second sentence means}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? Huh? What's wrong, Jabao-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Flawless. {katta?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling Jabao-san off like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrifying audacity! {no clue what's this dokubetsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the face of a grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider comparing yourself to the others someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, it's abnormal! {strangeness; abnormality; disorder​}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say, "abnormal?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for it, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's Pretty Boys Carnival special prize winner, \Nfirst president of the Dreamboats League,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the undisputed favorite \Nof the "Blonde Beauties of the World" convention,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate your "grandpa" insult! {.I won't tolerate you saying I have a grandpa face!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's an amazing find! \NOnce I've started, nobody can put up any resistance! {unbeatable; invincible; irresistible}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Best feeling ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Best feeling ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Iyona-chan's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna give me a lecture, young lady? \NFoisting your ostensible kindness again? {self-interested show of kindness; acting selfishly under the guise of kindness​}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad... What the hell am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lecturing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really any point for a woman as stuck-up as you \Nto try to understand the feelings of a deadbeat like me? {あんたみたいにお高くとまった女に俺のようなダメ男の気持ちがわかってたまるかよ }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just keep digging myself deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You casually succeed in everything you do, \Nmaking us earthly beings look miserable in comparison. {あんたは何をやってもうまくやっちまうから俺たち劣等性が悪く見られるんだぜ }
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta stop. Gotta stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The very existence of people like you is the root of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Good-Bad-kun off! \NThis is getting dangerous! {sounds like he's saying "taking them off is dangerous"} {それしてると危険!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized it myself a long time ago! {no clue what's word in the middle, bakkari?; also unsure which thing he realizes}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do it fast, you'll be under \Nthe slandering spell for the rest of your life! {/won't stop}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru. Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You think tears look good on your pretty face. \NYou just self-induced that, didn't you? {可愛い顔には涙が似合うと思って自分に因ってんじゃねえか? - no clue what he means, assumed "you're crying on your own volition to induce pity" TLC} {12:30: I'm hearing 可愛い顔には涙が似合うと思って自分によってんじゃねか？\NThe first part of the line you have works. As for the second part, I'm not sure.\NIt could be によって or に負って\Nhttps://jisho.org/word/%E8%B2%A0%E3%81%86}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother answering! \NI've no fancy for talking to the likes of you! {言えばいいだろう!あんたなんかと口ききたくないってさ! - hope he means this, tho first part could be "Don't be shy and say it!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Take off Good-Bad-kun, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to break into tears \Nand dash away from me to all four winds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know everyone else \Nwould welcome you with open arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, our poor sweet girl!" {again, unsure he means this} {可愛いととくだな!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Ain't no way! I need to take it off at once! \NThis is an item of unfathomable power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Still hasn't given up on me? {no clue what he means by まだ俺に用か?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just telling you the truth, nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst part of saying such horrible things to her \Nis that it feels so good! Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Hurry! Take them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you told me about it, I could understand. \NSo many things came to mind... {no clue what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so screwed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I said some terrible things \Nwhile under the spell of the spectacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurt you deeply, without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything of the kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you turn them around, you start seeing \Ngood about people and become all-loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come what may! {/will figure it out somehow}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan suddenly looks like an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This light, this warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I say something like that \Nto a divine being?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I deeply apologize for saying such lousy things. \NIyona-sama, is there any way I could make amends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you... Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time, I'm only thinking about myself. \NWhile you bestow the world with deep affection...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the light is too dazzling. \NI don't deserve to stay in your presence any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:15:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-san, Korekiyo-san, Ijigawa-san, Harako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are people of the highest virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And me... Me? \NHow may I ever come close to that? {unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Elementary school students \Ngrow like mushrooms these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out a spell, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't you teacher ever told you \Nnot to make detours on your way from school? {先生に下校中に道くさせちゃいけないって言われてますか} {/after dismissal}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. That's what the teacher said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher said so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-san and Ijigawa-san are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Lord, thank you so much \Nfor bestowing this chance upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You tryna start something with us? {/Do you want to have trouble with us?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Iyona-san and Rui-san, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please grant me this one favor and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, let Honmaru deal with all this. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, is that really you? {guess, assumed "omae tte" but no clue what it may mean; tlc just in case} {16:18: That's what I'm hearing too.\NLit is just "you...". Doesn't leave you much to work with though. - Aurelius}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please beat me up to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You pissed me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dreadful when I'm roused! {/angry}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For giving me this chance to make amends, \NI think you, gentlemen, are truly virtuous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right. {guess, iko iko?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel relieved now? {to be satisfied; to find peace of mind; to feel good}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nasty brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they able to understand \Nthe big words of a small man such as me? {absolutely no clue what's this all about, assuming he larps as buddha now or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true what they say about the elders \Nall being wonderful people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, where did you go? Me bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a single bad person in our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Taruruuto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, where were you? I've been looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry, Taruruuto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I assure you that not even for a moment, \NI've forgotten about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I lie to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a TV program I wanted to watch, \Nbut I've been made to run an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, please let me run it in your stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Going shopping, going shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shopping, shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my pleasure. {/Thank you for letting me go.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you send someone else instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No-no, I volunteered to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you embarrass us like that ever again! {/family}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so sorry! I've been inexcusably intrusive! {forward; officious; impertinent; intrusive}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep hitting me until you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe you've done something so unnecessary again! \NTsk! Hitting you only made me even madder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-kun, you're granting me forgiveness \Nafter just one beating? {ジャマー君 君はげんこつ一つで許してくれるのかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a virtuous man you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your frank and straightforward personality \Nis what I love the most about you! {君の竹をわったようなさっぱりした性格僕はとっても好きだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto-kun, there are no words \Nfor how marvelous these spectacles are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto-kun, thank you deeply \Nfor coming to my rescue time after time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a wonderful person you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful person...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I inflicted an irreparable wound on wonderful Harako-kun \Nby saying he has the face of a grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live if I don't make up for it somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto-kun, would you mind granting me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,can you give me a grandpa face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa face... {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Aging Pack. \NSacred Box Cream. {has to be reference to 玉手箱 but I don't see what semantic load it could have in this context}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But this magic is a little difficult to use. \NIt takes overnight to start working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we apply the pack like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you'll have a grown-up face tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, thank you for everything, Taruruuto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to return the favor one of these days. {hope he means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a grandpa face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be way too embarrassed to show up \Nbefore Iyona-chan and everyone, looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, what did you do this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, need to hurry! You'll be late again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto, I'll remember it, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, Honmaru. In order to soothe Harako, \Nyou asked me to give you the face of a grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Did I really say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, I ended up saying some nonsense \Nbecause of those spectacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I wear those spectacles with the other side out, \Nit's still a disastrous item!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not putting those spectacles on ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing the very same grandpa face as you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes us fellows, Harako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we have the same kind of face, \NI hope you're happy. {kinda "I went to the trouble of making it ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to affiliate with me.{/make fellows} \NNothing is grandpa-like about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. What's even the point of doing anything for anyone? {hope he means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Here we go again! {/gonna say something again}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why you've become so adult-like all around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, thank you so much for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And sorry we ran off without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda sorry for yesterday, Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I was the one who asked you to do the shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely hope to remain friends with you \Nfor the rest of my life. {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've suddenly become so cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you're really brave, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with a grandpa face on, \Nyou're still no match for me. {genuinely no idea what he means, TLC; was "なんだ やっぱ フケ顔の方がもてるんじゃね" in manga, which is kinda opposite of what he says here if I'm not mistaken} {22:12: I'm hearing 老け顔にかけちゃまだまだ俺の敵じゃないな\NThe line you have now is fine. \NBasically, Harako doesn't see Honmaru as a threat despite having a "grandpa face" too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! I'm insanely popular now thanks to that item! {popular person; favorite; favourite}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Spectacles that let you see people better! \NAin't they good? The best, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru seems happy. {choushi ii}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,An insanely dangerous transfer student comes to our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sure sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, she tries to mount an attack on Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But yesterday, when I just met her, \Nshe seemed like a kind, innocent girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun: \NZakenja Neyo. {could be it's already her name but usually they'd come up with kanji that sound exactly like the name and here it's still in kana; they did for her bro in the next ep so this gottta be the name too}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:04.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 40 \NZakenja Neyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's have a kendama duel!
